1. *Tata* dolazi sada kući. (Dad is coming home now.)
2. *Tati* smo rekli da se vratimo za sat vremena. (We told Dad to come back in an hour.)
3. *Tate* smo se oprostili pre nego što smo otišli. (We said goodbye to Dad before we left.)
4. Moj *tata* je dobar čovek. (My dad is a good man.)
5. *Tatu* volim mnogo. (I love Dad very much.)